Set API endpoint : 
cf api https://api.cf.eu10.hana.ondemand.com

Login : 
cf login (then enter your credentials)

List applications : 
cf apps (will give you the list of deployed application)

Get application UUID : 
cf app <app_name> --guid

Download  application (!!! the application must be running!!!): 
cf curl /v2/apps/<guid>/download > content.gz

Open content with 7zip :
https://downloads.sourceforge.net/project/portableapps/7-Zip%20Portable/7-ZipPortable_18.05.paf.exe?r=https%3A%2F%2Fsourceforge.net%2Fprojects%2Fportableapps%2Ffiles%2F7-Zip%2520Portable%2F7-ZipPortable_18.05.paf.exe%2Fdownload%3Fuse_mirror%3Dnetix&ts=1540201755)
